          "fill": "#444444",
          "content": "SPACING TOKENS\n4px — micro (icon-badge gap, password strength)\n6px — xs (label→input, SOAP heading→body, badge icon→text)\n8px — sm (header title→left, brand gap, card meta)\n10px — md (card list gap, card-group padding)\n12px — base (card internal gap, type scale gap)\n16px — lg (form field gap, section gaps, sidebar nav)\n20px — xl (content side padding, settings rows)\n24px — 2xl (signup content gap, dialog spacer)\n32px — 3xl (login form side padding)\n36px — 4xl (login content section gap)\n40px — 5xl (library padding, control bar padding)",
